&lt;h4&gt;Keeping you informed...&lt;/h4&gt;
	&lt;div class=&quot;blob&quot;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;blob-title&quot;&gt;
        Trump regime makes a habit of breaking the law &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.govtrack.us/posts/561/2025-12-19_congress-passes-laws-trump-administration-ignores-some-of-them&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;[Link&lt;span class=&quot;bi bi-link-45deg&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;]&lt;/a&gt;
