		&lt;p&gt;While most of the discussion centered around efforts to overthrow the election, Smith also discussed &quot;powerful evidence&quot; that Trump&#39;s storing of classified documents in his Florida residence was a deliberate obstruction of justice.&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;Smith has been under immense pressure from the unprecedented retribution campaign the Trump regime has mounted to (unsuccessfully) silence him.&lt;/p&gt;
