    &lt;div class=&quot;blob-title&quot;&gt;
        Two National Guard members shot, one killed in Washington D.C. &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.the-independent.com/news/world/americas/us-politics/national-guard-shooting-white-house-b2873256.html&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;[Link&lt;span class=&quot;bi bi-link-45deg&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;]&lt;/a&gt;
