        &lt;p&gt;This year, ICE-stapo agents have sent over 600 &lt;i&gt;children&lt;/i&gt; into the federal shelter system. That&#39;s more than the previous four years, &lt;b&gt;&lt;i&gt;combined,&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/b&gt; and more than any other single year in history. The Trump regime is targeting immigrant families, detaining parents and hauling their children off to shelters.&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;In Donny 2-Dolls&#39; first term, border agents made a practice of detaining adults and separating them from their children who were then detained in federal &quot;shelters.&quot; He stopped the practice after a massive public outcry and a lawsuit. But this year, he brought it back...with a vengeance.&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;The only difference is that now, instead of separating immigrant families at the border, Trump goon-squads are invading cities all across the country, rounding up friends and neighbors from our communities on the flimsiest pretexts they can come up with. If these detainees cannot offer immediate proof of their legal status, they are detained and their children are dumped in federal shelters. They are also making it harder than ever before for relatives or sponsors to get those children back again, with the average time spent in these &quot;shelters&quot; six times longer than it was during Biden&#39;s presidency.&lt;/p&gt;
