        House approves release of Epstein files 247-1 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/americas/us-politics/epstein-files-trump-signed-bill-what-happens-next-b2868740.html&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;[Link&lt;span class=&quot;bi bi-link-45deg&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;]&lt;/a&gt;
