                &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.usatoday.com/picture-gallery/news/nation/2025/11/06/sandwich-guy-not-guilty-assault-federal-officer-cultural-moment/87132759007/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;(USA Today) &quot;Sandwich guy&quot; not guilty of assaulting officer. See what the cultural moment inspired&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
