				&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2025/11/5/government-shutdown-becomes-longest-in-us-history-as-impact-felt-nationwide&quot; target-&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;(Al Jazeera) Government shutdown becomes longest in US history as impact felt nationwide&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
            &lt;/ul&gt;
