		&lt;p&gt;As the people grow hungry, Donny 2-Dolls is flaunting his wealth. But not just on his own property. He&#39;s continuing to build his palatial ballroom and bragging about his latest gaudy renovations to his bathroom in the White House.&lt;/p&gt;
