&lt;section class=&quot;block the-good&quot;&gt;
	&lt;h4&gt;The good...&lt;/h4&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;blob&quot;&gt;
        &lt;div class=&quot;blob-title&quot;&gt;
            No Kings Day 2.0: The largest protest in U.S. history &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WjSCy54LqaI&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;[Link&lt;span class=&quot;bi bi-link-45deg&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;]&lt;/a&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;div class=&quot;blob-content&quot;&gt;
            &lt;div&gt;
                &lt;p&gt;The largest protest in American history was held on October 18, 2025, when over 7 million Americans turned out to protest the Trump regime&#39;s systematic dismantling of American democracy.&lt;/p&gt;
                &lt;p&gt;Across the United States, massive crowds gathered to let the world know: &quot;We have no kings in America.&quot;&lt;/p&gt;
