		&lt;p&gt;But don&#39;t worry, because 2-faced 2-Dolls has also promised that he would pay for the project himself. Except, that&#39;s not true either: White House officials have recently released the list of individuals and corporations who &quot;contributed&quot; to the project, and Trump&#39;s name is not on the list.&lt;/p&gt;
