&lt;section class=&quot;block the-ugly&quot;&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;The ugly...&lt;/h4&gt;
	&lt;div class=&quot;blob&quot;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;blob-title&quot;&gt;
        The desperate plot to stop Mamdani &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=djzVYqZRdng&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;[Link&lt;span class=&quot;bi bi-link-45deg&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;]&lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;blob-content&quot;&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;Zohran Mamdani is one of the most popular political figures in the United States. He is also a Democratic Socialist like Bernie Sanders and Alexandria Ocasio-Cortez, who are also wildly popular political figures.&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;Mamdani is running on a platform of making New York more affordable to the people who live there. But pro-capitalist politicians and donors are not going to let him win without a fight. Top Democratic Party members are refusing to endorse Mamdani, despite the fact that he won the Democratic primary nomination. Republicans are doing everything they can to try to dig up real or imagined dirt on Mamdani, who they continue to refer to as a communist.&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;These anti-Mamdani efforts have nothing to do with political party. Instead, they come from wealthy Americans (of both parties) who are afraid that Mamdani-like candidates will threaten the balance of power. As the election grows closer, Mamdani&#39;s popularity continues to grow and the wealthy elite are growing more and more desperate. Wealthy donors are pouring money into campaign funds to support anyone other than Mamdani. Donny 2-Dolls has even promised to get involved, threatening to arrest and/or deport Mamdani if he is elected.&lt;/p&gt;
