&lt;section class=&quot;block the-bad&quot;&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;The bad...&lt;/h4&gt;
	&lt;div class=&quot;blob&quot;&gt;
        &lt;div class=&quot;blob-title&quot;&gt;Government shuts down without budget resolution &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/americas/us-politics/government-shutdown-senate-democrats-republicans-b2839062.html&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;[Link&lt;span class=&quot;bi bi-link-45deg&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;]&lt;/a&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;div class=&quot;blob-content&quot;&gt;
            &lt;div class=&quot;image-right&quot; style=&quot;width:225px&quot;&gt;
                &lt;img class=&quot;img-link&quot; alt=&quot;Sorry, we&#39;re closed&quot; loading=&quot;lazy&quot; decoding=&quot;async&quot; style=&quot;--img-width:200&quot; src=&quot;/images/ZpWMzwfFK0-200.webp&quot; width=&quot;200&quot; height=&quot;94&quot;&gt;
                &lt;p class=&quot;caption&quot;&gt;Image by &lt;a href=&quot;https://pixabay.com/users/geralt-9301/?utm_source=link-attribution&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=image&amp;utm_content=895398&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Gerd Altmann&lt;/a&gt; from &lt;a href=&quot;https://pixabay.com//?utm_source=link-attribution&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=image&amp;utm_content=895398&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Pixabay&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
            &lt;/div&gt;
            &lt;p&gt;The U.S. government has officially shut down as Congress fails to come to an agreement on a funding bill. Republicans expect Democrats to accept the funding bill they created without any Democratic feedback, and Democrats expect Republicans to make concessions and extend subsidies for Affordable Care Act health insurance policies for American citizens.&lt;/p&gt;
            &lt;p&gt;While the government is shut down, government employees will not receive their paychecks, except for Members of Congress who continue to be paid. Unpaid employees fall into two categories: Those that are temporarily ordered not to report to work, and those who are considered essential personnel and are required to continue working without pay. But Donny 2-Dolls is weighing the options for adding a third category: Just fire the furloughed employees. The Trump regime has been rashly firing federal employees since taking control of the country, and now they are using this shutdown to inflict even more pain on the American people.&lt;/p&gt;
            &lt;p&gt;While Democrats disagree with most of the provisions of the Republican spending bill, the main concession they are asking for is to extend subsidies for health insurance policies that are set to expire at the end of the year. If these subsidies expire, millions of Americans will see their health care policies double or even triple in price next year.&lt;/p&gt;
