        &lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;In one of many nightmarish scenes just this week, hundreds of armed ICE thugs wearing military-style costumes descended on an apartment complex in the middle of the night along with riot trucks and helicopters. They deployed smoke grenades, broke through fences and stormed the building, dragging residents out of their homes at gunpoint to stand outside in little to no clothing for hours or loading them like cattle into unmarked rental vans and hauling off to undisclosed locations.&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;Some of those rounded up may have been undocumented, but many of them were certainly legal U.S. residents. In all, 37 people were arrested. Children were tied together with zip-ties while agents laughed and one was heard to say, &quot;Fuck them kids.&quot;&lt;/p&gt;
