&lt;p&gt;Recap of this week in the revolution: ICE assault on congressional candidate and imprisoned journalist to be deported. Trump pushes unfounded Tylenol warnings, Pentagon requires journalists to sign pledge not to gather information, and Hegseth&amp;#39;s plan to remove Black men from military service. Meidas Touch finds Trump&amp;#39;s economic plan hidden in plain sight.&lt;/p&gt;


