		&lt;p&gt;Guevara&#39;s son, Oscar, is trying to keep his father&#39;s online news service running, but suffers from a brain tumor and is struggling to make ends meet. He and his sister have had to start a GoFundMe campaign to try to make ends meet with their father in prison.&lt;/p&gt;
