				&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.cbsnews.com/newyork/news/nyc-officials-arrested-ice-protest/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;(CBS) New York officials among dozens arrested at anti-ICE demonstration&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
