				&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.thenation.com/article/society/charlie-kirk-assassination-tragedy/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;(The Nation) Let&#39;s not forget who Charlie Kirk really was&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
