		&lt;p&gt;Texas has already approved their redistricting map, and California has promised to retaliate, although they are actually waiting for voter approval before making changes. Missouri is the third state to enter the fray, though several other states are planning to join the war at some point before the 2026 primaries.&lt;/p&gt;
