					&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.npr.org/2025/09/11/nx-s1-5538448/senate-republicans-nuclear-option-confirmations&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;(NPR) Senate Republicans turn to &quot;nuclear option&quot; to speed confirmation of Trump nominees&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
					&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.nbcnews.com/politics/congress/senate-republicans-nuclear-option-change-rules-trump-nominees-rcna230565&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;(NBC) Senate Republicans trigger &quot;nuclear option,&quot; changing rules to speed up Trump nominees&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
